{"tid":2183724,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"知專生不敢報警 林卓廷助出庭","createTime":"2020-09-01T05:53:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T06:12:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"52bff63780b540f17bed448f33485d1ab6b70b1b","tid":2183724,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:53:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/7G67BC2X2ZDGRH5AEXH3GG6UWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2F7G67BC2X2ZDGRH5AEXH3GG6UWI%2F&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7lQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=3908a61b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2F7G67BC2X2ZDGRH5AEXH3GG6UWI%2F&h=140c40bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/7G67BC2X2ZDGRH5AEXH3GG6UWI/</a><br />\n<br />\n知專生不敢報警 林卓廷助出庭<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】死因庭昨加插了一名證人，事緣研訊主任上周五收到立法會議員林卓廷辦事處的電郵，稱一名知專男生疑於彥霖失蹤當天發現她蹤影，希望作證。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警員︰彥霖初被指死因可疑 上級僅列屍體發現  但或涉刑事轉介跟進<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。「好似搵緊人咁」，女子最終朝B出口方向離開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n擔心自身安全<br />\n<br />\n研訊主任播放閉路電視片段，顯示彥霖當晚約7時10分現身善明邨邨口，這是她最後被攝下的身影。陳自言當時仍在校，又稱該邨口至調景嶺站的步程在五分鐘之內。<br />\n<br />\n死因裁判官高偉雄問陳，為何不及早提供資訊。陳稱不信任警方，因警方將案件列為屍體發現案而非謀殺案，做法不合理，加上擔心自身安全，只好由議員及法庭協調出庭。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，公眾對本案疑慮重重，現在召開死因研訊「算遲」。惟裁判官指，搜證及索取口供需時，本案已算迅速開審，又稱：「相信你個名已經被廣泛報道，唔需要擔心人身安全」。"},{"pid":"de704267ac8679c3c9e5f506bc272455963c0021","tid":2183724,"uid":366932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221441f1a1a452e9b4480cbc45131375ec18d2af","tid":2183724,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:57:20.000Z","msg":"黨媒truth hk又出fake news 又用721微博假圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2183510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2183510</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0894f89caab7f1d27a9c2e2cab7a80f6e423a5b9","tid":2183724,"uid":103363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:58:43.000Z","msg":"廣泛報道就唔需要驚人身安全咩?"},{"pid":"38594d41aba0b042a213a708f195950b368522f8","tid":2183724,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:12:11.000Z","msg":"有d連登仔只係識屌泛民，呢d場合就會潛水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}